# Data — the market-state raw pulls ARE committed on purpose: they are public
# market data (index/VIX closes) and the reproducibility anchor so a reader can
# run `make all` without DB credentials (§8.5). Only large per-name price dumps
# (Phase 2, data/prices/) stay out of git.
/data/prices/

# Generated figures are reproducible from the pipeline; keep the dir, ignore output.
/figures/*.png
!/figures/.gitkeep

# local tooling config
.claude/
*.log
